            PTCLTool is a tool for editing the .ptcl particle effect format used in various Nintendo 3DS games, including:
    
            Animal Crossing: New Leaf
            Mario Kart 7
            New Super Mario Bros. 2
            Photos with Mario
            Photos with Animal Crossing
            Super Mario 3D Land
            いっしょにフォト ピクミン
